---
layout: base.njk
title: Home
description: Practical SEO, content, and campaign tools for clearer writing and smarter execution.
permalink: /
---

<section class="hero-shell">
  <div class="container hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <h1>SEO and content tools that help you work faster.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        Use simple tools for writing, readability, metadata, and campaign tasks — then go deeper with practical guides when you need more context.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="/tools/" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Tools</a>
        <a href="/articles/" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Guides</a>
      </div>

      <ul class="hero-points">
        <li>No sign-up required for core tools</li>
        <li>Built for SEO, content, and campaign workflows</li>
        <li>Simple pages with clean, shareable URLs</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-panel">
      <div class="hero-card hero-card-main">
        <span class="mini-label">Popular tools</span>
        <div class="hero-tool-list">
          {% for tool in tools %}
            {% if tool.featured and loop.index <= 3 %}
              <a class="hero-tool-item" href="{{ tool.url }}">
                <span>
                  <strong>{{ tool.name }}</strong>
                  <small>{{ tool.category }}</small>
                </span>
                <em>{{ tool.cta }}</em>
              </a>
            {% endif %}
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="hero-support">
  <div class="container hero-support-grid">
    <div class="hero-card mini-stat">
      <span class="mini-label">Focus</span>
      <strong>SEO + Content</strong>
      <p>Practical utilities for writing, metadata, and campaign support.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-card mini-stat">
      <span class="mini-label">Structure</span>
      <strong>Tools + Articles</strong>
      <p>Use a tool first, then continue into a guide for better execution.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="trust-strip">
  <div class="container trust-row">
    <div class="trust-item">
      <strong>Practical output</strong>
      <span>Focused tools for real writing and marketing tasks.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <strong>Cleaner workflows</strong>
      <span>Move from quick checks to deeper guidance without friction.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="trust-item">
      <strong>Built to scale</strong>
      <span>Structured for more tools, articles, and internal linking.</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head section-head-split">
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Featured Tools</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Start with the core tool set.</h2>
      </div>
      <p class="section-desc">
        These highlighted tools are the fastest entry points for readability, writing checks, metadata work, and campaign support.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-grid">
      {% for tool in tools %}
        {% if tool.featured %}
          <article class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-top">
              <span class="feature-tag">{{ tool.category or "Tool" }}</span>
              <a href="{{ tool.url }}" class="feature-link">Open tool</a>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-body">
              <h3>{{ tool.name }}</h3>
              <p>{{ tool.description }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-bottom">
              <span class="feature-meta">Free to use</span>
              <a href="{{ tool.url }}" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">{{ tool.cta }}</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-soft">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="dual-panel">
      <div class="info-panel">
        <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">Action first. Learning second.</h2>
        <p class="section-desc">
          The site is designed so a visitor can solve a task quickly, then continue into related content when they want more context.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="steps-panel">
        <div class="step-card">
          <strong>1. Pick a tool</strong>
          <p>Start with the task you need to complete right now.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <strong>2. Get the result</strong>
          <p>Use a focused interface without extra noise or clutter.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-card">
          <strong>3. Read the guide</strong>
          <p>Move into articles that explain the topic in a simple way.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>